**Telegram (Send Message):**
```
{
  "parameters": {
    "chatId": "={{ $json.chat_id }}",
    "text": "={{ $json.message }}",
    "additionalFields": {"parse_mode": "Markdown"}
  },
  "type": "n8n-nodes-base.telegram",
  "typeVersion": 1.2,
  "position": [1760, 0],
  "id": "uuid-here",
  "name": "Send Telegram",
  "credentials": {"telegramApi": {"id": "YOUR_CREDENTIAL_ID", "name": "Telegram account"}}
